artists.strBiographyEN: see also: John Barry, John Barry Orchestra  The John Barry Orchestra was led by John Barry (born john Barry Prendergast, in 1933). The orchestra is probably best known for the film music of On Her Majesty's Secret Service, a James Bond Movie. Besides this movie soundtrack, Barry composed the music for about 13 other Bond movies.  Furthermore, John Barry composed the music for dozens of movies and television series, including: Out of Africa and Dances With Wolves.   More info about John barry and his orchestra can be found at: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/John_Barry_(composer)
